323
00:28:25,319 --> 00:28:28,339
[SPEAKER_00] I tek nakon što napravio sve,

324
00:28:28,339 --> 00:28:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] ide moliti Bogu.

325
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] Što znači da kad ti stojiš pred neki izazov,

326
00:28:34,039 --> 00:28:37,960
